
SOLUTION

questions:

how are lines given ? a,b,c or point and vector or point and normal vector ?
how big are numbers ?
how small are numbers ?
float ? int ? 
precision ? epsilon ?

solution:

a1x + b1y + c = 0
a2x + b2y + c = 0

det = a1b2 - a2b1
detx = c1b2 - c2b1
dety = a1c2 - c2a1

if (det != 0) intersect
if (det == 0 && detx == 0 && dety == 0) same

otherwise parallel 
